<%- include('layout-top') %>
<section class="hero"><h1>Willkommen im Premium Shop</h1><p>Produkte auswählen, Bestellung aufgeben und Übergabe direkt über die Website abstimmen.</p></section>
<section class="panel">
  <h2>Kategorien und Sortierung</h2>
  <div class="chips"><a class="chip <%= !selectedCategory ? 'active' : '' %>" href="/?sort=<%= sort || 'created_desc' %>">Alle</a><% categories.forEach(c => { %><a class="chip <%= selectedCategory===c.id ? 'active' : '' %>" href="/?kategorie=<%= c.id %>&sort=<%= sort || 'created_desc' %>"><%= c.name %></a><% }) %></div>
  <form method="get" action="/" class="inline" style="margin-top:12px">
    <% if (selectedCategory) { %><input type="hidden" name="kategorie" value="<%= selectedCategory %>"><% } %>
    <label>Sortieren nach
      <select name="sort" onchange="this.form.submit()">
        <option value="created_desc" <%= sort==='created_desc'?'selected':'' %>>Neueste zuerst</option>
        <option value="price_asc" <%= sort==='price_asc'?'selected':'' %>>Preis aufsteigend</option>
        <option value="price_desc" <%= sort==='price_desc'?'selected':'' %>>Preis absteigend</option>
        <option value="name_asc" <%= sort==='name_asc'?'selected':'' %>>Name A–Z</option>
        <option value="name_desc" <%= sort==='name_desc'?'selected':'' %>>Name Z–A</option>
        <option value="views_desc" <%= sort==='views_desc'?'selected':'' %>>Meist betrachtet</option>
      </select>
    </label>
  </form>
</section>
<div class="grid">
<% products.forEach(p => { const variants = (p.variants || []).filter(v=>v.active); const stock = variants.length ? variants.reduce((s,v)=>s+Number(v.stock||0),0) : p.stock; const isGift=p.product_type==='gift_card'; %>
  <article class="card product <%= isGift?'gift-product-card':'' %>">
    <a class="product-image-box" href="/produkte/<%= p.id %>"><% if (p.image_url) { %><img class="product-image" src="<%= p.image_url %>" alt="<%= p.name %>"><% } else if(isGift){ %><div class="gift-placeholder">🎁<span>Geschenkgutschein</span></div><% } else { %><div class="placeholder">Kein Bild</div><% } %></a>
    <p class="muted"><%= p.category_name || 'Allgemein' %><% if (p.age_level && p.age_level>0) { %> · <span class="sale"><%= p.age_level %>+</span><% } %></p>
    <h2><a href="/produkte/<%= p.id %>"><%= p.name %></a></h2>
    <p class="product-description fit-description" data-fit-text><%= p.description %></p>
    <% if (isGift) { %>
      <p><b>Wert frei wählbar</b><br><span class="muted"><%= money(p.gift_card_min_cents||500) %> bis <%= money(p.gift_card_max_cents||50000) %></span></p>
      <a class="btn" href="/produkte/<%= p.id %>">Gutschein gestalten</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <% if (variants.length) { %><p class="muted">Sorten: <%= variants.map(v => v.name + ' (' + v.stock + ')').join(', ') %></p><% } %>
      <p><% if (p.discount_percent > 0) { %><span class="old"><%= money(p.price_cents) %></span> <b><%= money(discounted(p)) %></b> <span class="sale">−<%= p.discount_percent %>%</span><% } else { %><b><%= money(p.price_cents) %></b><% } %></p>
      <p class="muted">Lager: <%= stock %> · Aufrufe: <%= p.views_count || 0 %></p>
      <% if (p.supplier_status === 'out_of_stock') { %><p class="error">Nicht auf Lager</p><% } %>
      <% if (isCustomer) { %><form method="post" action="/cart/add/<%= p.id %>" class="stack compact"><% if (variants.length) { %><select name="variant_id" required><option value="">Sorte wählen</option><% variants.forEach(v => { %><option value="<%= v.id %>"><%= v.name %> · Lager <%= v.stock %></option><% }) %></select><% } %><div class="inline"><input type="number" name="quantity" min="1" max="<%= stock %>" value="1"><button <%= stock<=0?'disabled':'' %>>In den Warenkorb</button></div></form>
      <% } else if (!user) { %><a class="btn" href="/login">Zum Kaufen einloggen</a><% } %>
    <% } %>
  </article>
<% }) %>
</div>
<%- include('layout-bottom') %>
